{
  "stem": "942.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was able to go to the wascherei, for instance, and get some clean clothes, you see, because there were clothes there that were cleaned that were shipped back to Germany all the time, you know, from transports, you see.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I had some underwear, you know, I had some shirts, and I had better stuff, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was, you know-- you couldn't do this otherwise.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could never walk in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But here I am, an official.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm coming from the operating room with all these gowns, you know, and I'm doing a service.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was able to-- and I was able to, if I had some pills, I was able to barter with some pills, you know, to get some food, you see.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I'm cleaning, I'm sterilizing instruments, and you know, I was eventually preparing people for their operations, you know, like, shaving, you know, the people, and putting the gowns on.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And most of the operations were a lot of hernia operations, here, and many bad accidents, people that were badly hurt on the job, or from shooting, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had, we had ether.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, we had novocaine to put people out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were usually, if they operated on a hernia or a lower part, they were giving them spinal.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had no blood plasma, but we had instruments.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a, a x-ray machine there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The doctors that were operating were two Polish doctors, gentile doctors.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember one name, a Dr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Orzeszko. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Orzeszko, ?] I think it means a nut.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was the chief surgeon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was a Polish political prisoner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And his assistant was a Polish political prisoner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you know, they used to get parcels from home.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
